Package: flmam 
Version: 0.98.0
Date: 2018-09-01
Title: Fit Linear Models On Any Matrix Representation
Authors@R: c(person("Aaron", "Lun", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        email="alun@wehi.edu.au"))
Depends: R (>= 3.5), BiocParallel
Imports: Rcpp, stats, methods
Suggests: testthat, BiocStyle, knitr, rmarkdown, beachmat,
    HDF5Array, DelayedArray
biocViews: Clustering, Classification
Description: Fits linear models on any matrix representation
    including sparse matrices and HDF5-backed matrices, without
    requiring explicit realization to a dense array.
    Parallelization is achieved using the BiocParallel framework.
License: GPL-3
LinkingTo: Rcpp, beachmat, Rhdf5lib
VignetteBuilder: knitr
SystemRequirements: C++11
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
